sub_title:
TU Delft,
Master of Science Architecture, Urbanism and Building Sciences
summary:
Landscape architecture brings forth optimism, where the transformative power of nature merges with human creativity, fostering vibrant and sustainable environments that inspire and uplift communities.

I am passionate to create a harmonious and liveable environment for all; for humans, flora and fauna, through leveraging on science and technology. This allows constraints to be transformed into opportunities where we can work with natural processes to develop sustainable designs and systems solutions.
